Q Q02                            FLD  [1264]         --> [13.10]         Type=MFLD    Max=10
X  1st=[13]                 2nd=[14]                 3rd=[15]
X  4th=[16]                 5th=[17]                 6th=[18]
X  7th=[19]                 8th=[20]                 9th=[21]
X 10th=[22]
T DATAFROM(0.1) GROUP: ANSWERFROM(GROUP)ID_DSS: ANSWERFROM(ID_DSS)  (DATAFROM(0.1)) DATAFROM(0.1) - DATAFROM(0.1)
T  
T 02. Interviewer Record: What were the instructions and advice given to you by the recording/auto-attendant?
T  
T (SELECT ALL THAT APPLY)
T  
R     A                                                             Recording intercepted by a live person
R     B                                                             Hang up, dial 911 or go to nearest ER
R     C                                                             Go to an urgent care center
R     D                                                             Told to press # or stay on the line to be connected to a provider or nurse
R     E                                                             Told to press # or stay on the line to speak to an after hours service representative
R     F                                                             Caller is able to leave a message with a call back within 30 minutes
R     G                                                             Recorded message provides a phone number for the physician or on-call physician or nurse
R     H                                                             Directed to call during regular business hours
R     I                                                             Other (SPECIFY)
R     J                                                             No instructions provided by the recording/auto attendant.

