Q QINTRO                         FLD  [1433]         --> [24]
T DATAFROM(0.1) GROUP: ANSWERFROM(GROUP)ID_DSS: ANSWERFROM(ID_DSS)  (DATAFROM(0.1)) DATAFROM(0.1) - DATAFROM(0.1)
T  
T Hello, I'm with Press Ganey calling on behalf of Texas Children's Health Plan. We are calling to assess the after-hours service and protocol. For quality and training purposes, this call may be recorded. Could you confirm that this is the after-hours service line for ANSWERFROM(PHONE_CONTACT)
T  
R     1                                                             Yes
R     2                                                             No

Q Q04                            FLD  [1457]         --> [25.8]          Type=MFLD    Max=8
X  1st=[25]                 2nd=[26]                 3rd=[27]
X  4th=[28]                 5th=[29]                 6th=[30]
X  7th=[31]                 8th=[32]
T DATAFROM(0.1) GROUP: ANSWERFROM(GROUP)ID_DSS: ANSWERFROM(ID_DSS)  (DATAFROM(0.1)) DATAFROM(0.1) - DATAFROM(0.1)
T  
T 04. What would you tell a patient calling with a "non-emergency" situation at this time?
T  
T LISTEN CAREFULLY TO RESPONSE.
T  
T Non-Emergency examples:  1) Change in a current condition under treatment by the physician. 2) Parent is unable to assess the condition.
T  
R     A                                                             Hang up, dial 911 or go to nearest ER
R     B                                                             Go to an urgent care center
R     C                                                             Will connect caller to a provider or nurse
R     D                                                             Will ask caller to leave their name and number, someone will call them back within 1 hour
R     E                                                             Will provide the caller with phone number to contact their physician or on-call physician or nurse
R     F                                                             Will take caller information and give to the doctor or on-call physician or nurse to call back within 1 hour
R     G                                                             Other (Specify)
R     H                                                             Don't know (DO NOT READ)

